      <rules>
        <rule name="Death Company" id="b38e-27f6-e76a-3ca5" hidden="false">
          <description>Instead of an Honour Guard, a Blood Angels Chaplain is always accompanied by D3+3 Death Company Space Marines. If the Death Company are equipped with jump packs, the Chaplain must also be equipped with a jump pack.</description>
