              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">The Death Mask of Sanguinius follows the standard rules for Death Masks.
In addition, any enemy squad within 6&quot; of Dante at the start of that side&apos;s turn must pass a Morale check or immediately start falling back. A -1 modifier for being below half strength applies.</characteristic>
